Package: mvpcran
Type: Package
Title: CRAN on a stick
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2017-03-06
Authors@R: c(
  person('Thomas Lin', 'Pedersen', email = 'thomasp85@gmail.com', role = c('aut', 'cre')),
  person("Bob", "Rudis", email = "bob@rud.is", role = c("aut", "cre"))
)
Maintainer: Thomas Lin Pedersen <thomasp85@gmail.com>
Description: In some situations it is nice to have access to a portable version
  of CRAN, e.g. if network access is spotty. 'mvpcran' (Minimum Viable, Portable
  CRAN) contains functionality for creating and updating a local CRAN mirror 
  that can be put on a USB stick or a portable drive.
License: GPL (>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
